MonoBehaviour:
  m_ObjectHideFlags: 0
  m_CorrespondingSourceObject: {fileID: 0}
  m_PrefabInstance: {fileID: 0}
  m_PrefabAsset: {fileID: 0}
  m_GameObject: {fileID: 1480489200}
  m_Enabled: 1
  m_EditorHideFlags: 0
  m_Script: {fileID: 11500000, guid: f82f270ba063f1441945b68b0555d5a2, type: 3}
  m_Name: 
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: 
  npcName: Jarkov
  isFirstNPC: 0
  dialogueLines: []
  isQuestNPC: 1
  questDialogue:
  - The name's Jarkov.
  - You must be looking for the beastial usurper.
  - I am only asking is for you to retrieve me an ancient scroll from the dark forest.
  - Be careful, the forest is haunted by spirits of the dead.
  - Retrieve the scroll and I can help you defeat the usurper.
  completedDialogue:
  - You found the scroll from the dark woods!
  - This scroll holds the weakness to the usurper, many villagers were vanished in
    search of this.
  - Aha! I see it now. For someone to defeat the usurper, they need to have the mighty
    blue sword.
  - 'So you are the chosen one who will save us from the beast. '
  - The usurper is mostly seen near the lake which is around the cave you were settled
    in.
  - You can find the usurper there and defeat it. Godspeed!
  interactPopup: {fileID: 1417610831}
